  <body style="font-family: 'Poppins'">
    <%- include('../partials/nav') %>
    <div
      id="carouselExampleCaptions"
      class="carousel slide"
      data-bs-ride="carousel"
    >
      <div class="carousel-indicators">
        <button
          type="button"
          data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions"
          data-bs-slide-to="0"
          class="active"
          aria-current="true"
          aria-label="Slide 1"
        ></button>
        <button
          type="button"
          data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions"
          data-bs-slide-to="1"
          aria-label="Slide 2"
        ></button>
        <button
          type="button"
          data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions"
          data-bs-slide-to="2"
          aria-label="Slide 3"
        ></button>
      </div>
      <div class="carousel-inner wp-caption" style="max-height: 31rem;">
        <div class="carousel-item active">
          <img
            src="/img/home-slide-1.jpg"
            class="d-block w-100"
            alt="..."
            style="max-height: 31rem;"
          />
          <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
            <h4 class="wp-caption-text">
              “Competence without compassion is worthless. Compassion without
              competence is meaningless”
            </h4>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item" style="max-height: 31rem;"> 
          <img
            src="/img/home-slide-two.jpg"
            class="d-block w-100"
            alt="..."
          />
          <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
            <h4 class="wp-caption-text">
              “If the human brain were so simple that we could understand it, we
              would be so simple that we couldn’t.” – Emerson M. Pugh
            </h4>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item" style="max-height: 31rem;">
          <img
            src="/img/home-slide-3.jpg"
            class="d-block w-100"
            alt="..."
          />
          <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
            <h4 class="wp-caption-text">
              "Embark on a journey through the intricate neural pathways of the
              brain, where complexity unveils a captivating puzzle, inviting us
              to unravel its wonders with awe and curiosity."
            </h4>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <button
        class="carousel-control-prev"
        type="button"
        data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions"
        data-bs-slide="prev"
      >
        <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="visually-hidden">Previous</span>
      </button>
      <button
        class="carousel-control-next"
        type="button"
        data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions"
        data-bs-slide="next"
      >
        <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
      </button>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
      <br /><br /><br />
      <div id="events">
        <h2 style="font-family: 'Lora'; text-align: center; font-weight: bold;">
          Upcoming Events
        </h2>
        <br />
        <div class="row col-md-12">
          <% events.forEach(event => { %>        
            <div class="col-md-4">
              <a href="/<%=event.url %>" style="color:#000000" ><div
                class="card mb-3 box-shadow"
                style="
                  box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15) 1.5px 1.5px 2.6px;
                  border: none;
                "
              >
                <img
                  class="card-img-top"
                  alt=""
                  style="height: 320px;"
                  src="/img/<%= event.image %>"
                  data-holder-rendered="true"
                />
                <div class="card-body">
                  <p class="card-text">
                    <%= event.title %>
                  </p>
                  <div class="row col-md-12">
                    <div class="col-md-8">
                      <div class="row">
                        <i
                          class="fa-regular fa-calendar col-md-2 "
                          style="color: gray"
                        ></i>
                        <p class="col-md-10 text-nowrap" style="font-size: 0.9rem; color: gray">
                          <%= event.date %>
                        </p>
                      </div>
                      <div class="row">
                        <i
                          class="fa-regular fa-clock col-md-2"
                          style="color: gray"
                        ></i>
                        <p class="col-md-10 text-nowrap" style="font-size: 0.9rem; color: gray">
                          <%= event.time %>
                        </p>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-4 ">
                      
                      
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div></a>
            </div>
          <% }) %>
          
          
          
        </div>
      </div>
      <br /><br /><br />

      <div id="goals" style="margin-left: 3rem;">
        <h2 style="font-family: 'Lora'; text-align: center; font-weight: bold">
          Vision
        </h2>
        <br />
        <div class="row col-md-12 m-3">
          <div class="row col-md-4 p-3 ">
          <div class="card text-center col-md-12"
            style="
              background-color: #fcfcfc;
              box-shadow: rgba(99, 99, 99, 0.2) 0px 2px 8px 0px;
              border: none;
            "
          >
            <div class="card-body">
              <i
                class="fa-solid fa-chalkboard-user"
                style="
                  color: gray;
                  font-size: 50px;
                  padding-bottom: 20px;
                  padding-top: 25px;
                "
              ></i>
              <p class="card-title" style="margin-bottom: 0px">
                <b>Seminars for Students</b>
              </p>
              <p class="card-text">
                <small
                  >We organize seminars to enrich medical students' grasp of
                  neurology and neurosurgery, offering valuable insights into
                  these specialties
                </small>
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          </div>
         
          <div class="row col-md-4 p-3">
          <div class="card text-center col-md-12"
            style="
              background-color: #fcfcfc;
              box-shadow: rgba(99, 99, 99, 0.2) 0px 2px 8px 0px;
              border: none;
              
            "
          >
            <div class="card-body col-md-12">
              <i
                class="fa-solid fa-users"
                style="
                  color: gray;
                  font-size: 50px;
                  padding-bottom: 20px;
                  padding-top: 25px;
                "
              ></i>
              <p class="card-title" style="margin-bottom: 0px">
                <b>Neurology and Neurosurgery Conferences</b>
              </p>
              <p class="card-text">
                <small
                  >NEUROMER hosts impactful conferences uniting students and
                  professionals, fostering knowledge exchange and networking
                </small>
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="row col-md-4 p-3">
          <div class="card text-center col-md-12"
            style="
              background-color: #fcfcfc;
              box-shadow: rgba(99, 99, 99, 0.2) 0px 2px 8px 0px;
              border: none;
              
            "
          >
            <div class="card-body">
              <i
                class="fa-solid fa-user-doctor"
                style="
                  color: gray;
                  font-size: 50px;
                  padding-bottom: 20px;
                  padding-top: 25px;
                "
              ></i>
              <p class="card-title" style="margin-bottom: 0px">
                <b>Networking with Doctors</b>
              </p>
              <p class="card-text">
                <small
                  >Our platform connects members with neurology and neurosurgery
                  experts, offering unique mentorship and career guidance
                </small>
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          </div>
          
        </div>
      </div>
      <br /><br /><br />

      <div id="statics">
        <h2 style="font-family: 'Lora'; text-align: center; font-weight: bold">
          Statistics
        </h2>
        <br />
        <div
          class="row col-md-12"
          style="
            background-color: #fcfcfc;
            box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15) 1.5px 1.5px 2.6px;
            border: none;
            padding: 20px 0 20px;
            border-radius: 25px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: row;
          "
        >

          <div class="col-md-4 p-3">
            <div class="row col-md-12 text-nowrap text-center" style="display: flex;flex-direction: column;">
              <span class="col-md-6" style="font-size: 50px;">60+</span>
              <span class="col-md-6" style="font-size: 30px;">Members</span>
            </div>
           
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-4 p-3">
            <div class="row col-md-12 text-nowrap text-center " style="display: flex;flex-direction: column;">
              <span class="col-md-6" style="font-size: 50px;">10+</span>
              <span class="col-md-6" style="font-size: 30px;">Countries</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-4 p-3">
            <div class="row col-md-12 text-nowrap text-center" style="display: flex;flex-direction: column;">
              <span class="col-md-6" style="font-size: 50px;">5</span>
              <span class="col-md-6" style="font-size: 30px;">Active Research</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <br /><br /><br />
      <div id="publication">
        <h2 style="font-family: 'Lora'; text-align: center; font-weight: bold">
          Publication
        </h2>
        <br /><br /><br />
        <div class="row col-md-12">
          <div class="row col-md-8 p-3">
            <img
              src="/img/publication_8.webp"
              alt=""
              
            />
          </div>
          
          <div class=" col-md-4 p-3">
            <br />
            <h3>Alice's Magical Mind: The Wonderland of Perceptions</h3>
            <br />
            <p>
              In 1907, the great British neurologist William Gowers reported
              epilepsy patients who perceived objects to look “twice their size”
              during the aura preceding their seizures. It is called...
            </p>
            <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary">Read more</button>
          </div>
        </div>
        <br /><br />
        <div class="row col-md-12">
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <br />
            <h3>
              Neuralink: Pioneering Potential in the Treatment of Alzheimer's
              Disease
            </h3>
            <br />
            <p>
              In a recent huge achievement on June 9, 2023, Neuralink,
              co-founded by Elon Musk, has received FDA approval for human
              trials involving the implantation of brain chips. This
              groundbreaking technology brings a new ray of hope for ...
            </p>
            <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary">Read more</button>
          </div>

          <div class="row col-md-6 p-3">
            <img
              src="/img/publication_7.jpg"
              alt=""
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <br /><br /><br />
    <%- include('../partials/footer') %>
